Civilization *Indus Valley School of Art and Architecture, Karachi, Pakistan
*International Valuation Standards, technical and ethical standards for the
conduct of valuations *International Vedanta Society, an Advaita Vedantic
organization based in India
* International Voluntary Service, the British branch of Service Civil
